{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"b7925b35f5","title":"新华书店上海发行所请示有关右派分子著作物的出版发行问题","origin":"上海市档案馆，A22-1-305，第10页","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"2ef562b2d7","index":0,"year":1957,"month":8,"day":10,"articleId":"b7925b35f5"}],"tags":[{"id":"7aac50a8c5","name":"文艺战线","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"cf057e367e","type":"title","text":"新华书店上海发行所请示有关右派分子著作物的出版发行问题","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b7925b35f5"},{"id":"28cb71ee5c","type":"appellation","text":"上海市出版局：","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b7925b35f5"},{"id":"640479a3b9","type":"paragraph","text":"当前反击右派斗争中，出版界内已揭露的许君远、仇标、王若望等一些作家右派分子，他们过去都有著作物出版发行，有些新书出版社还在继续征订，准备出版，如王若望的新著“上海来的人”，新文艺出版社最近交来内容简介，我们拟与该社联系后暂缓布置订货。兹请示有关问题如下：","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b7925b35f5"},{"id":"3f5a971744","type":"paragraph","text":"1、右派分子原有著作物，存书是否仍可继续发行，如遇售缺而读者读有需要时，可否重印。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b7925b35f5"},{"id":"ba5c4c89ee","type":"paragraph","text":"2、右派分子编著的出版新书，出版社交来内容介绍材料，我们是否仍可布置定货发行。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b7925b35f5"},{"id":"2ae303f590","type":"paragraph","text":"3、右派分子用笔名发表的著作，如何辨别处理。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b7925b35f5"},{"id":"6365591429","type":"paragraph","text":"以上几点，请予指示，俾有遵循。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b7925b35f5"},{"id":"01dc21d1b9","type":"paragraph","text":" 新华书店上海发行所（签章）1957年8月10日","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b7925b35f5"},{"id":"9b380dd304","type":"paragraph","text":"抄致：上海市委宣传部总店","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b7925b35f5"},{"id":"c92b9a057f","type":"paragraph","text":"编号：1967中共上海市委宣传部收文","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b7925b35f5"}],"page":{"id":"a02c9d6113","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"b7925b35f5","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}